cs.AR, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.ET, cs.DC

This paper is about implementing convolutional neural networks (CNNs) on VLSI chips, which is a topic related to computer architecture (cs.AR) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses memory optimization techniques, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) and embedded systems (cs.ET). Finally, the paper presents a reconfigurable processor, which is a topic related to digital circuits (cs.DC).
